ok 2017\"/><ref name=\"Bundesverband Musikindustrie: Internationales\"/>\n\n* [[Recording Industry Association of America|United States]]: 1958<ref name=\"History of the Awards\">{{cite web|url=https://www.riaa.com/gold-platinum/story/|title=History of the Awards|publisher=[[Recording Industry Association of America]]|accessdate=August 6, 2011}}</ref>\n* [[Recording Industry Association of Japan|Japan]]: 1989<ref name=\"About RIAJ: History\">{{cite web|url=http://www.riaj.or.jp/f/e/about/history.html|title=About RIAJ: History|publisher=[[Recording Industry Association of Japan]]|accessdate=November 8, 2015}}</ref>\n* [[Bundesverband Musikindustrie|Germany]]: 1975<ref name=\"BVMI Certifications\">{{cite web|url=https://www.musikindustrie.de/markt-bestseller/gold-/platin-und-diamond-auszeichnung/datenbank|title=BVMI: Gold-/Platin-Datenbank|publisher=[[Bundesverband Musikindustrie]]|accessdate=August 5, 2019}}</ref>\n* [[British Phonographic Industry|United Kingdom]]: 1973<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bpi.co.uk/bpi-awards/about-bpi-awards/|title=About BPI Awards|publisher=[[British Phonographic Industry]]|accessdate=November 7, 2017}}</ref>\n* [[Syndicat National de l'\u00c9dition Phonographique|France]]: 1973<ref name=\"Les Certifications Officielles: Chronologie Albums\"/>\n* [[Music Canada|Canada]]: 1975<ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/?id=qCQEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PT58&dq=CRIA+Gold+and+Platinum+1975#v=onepage&q=CRIA%20Gold%20and%20Platinum%201975&f=false|title=CRIA|work=Billboard|accessdate=July 1, 2014|date=October 2, 1976|last1=Nielsen Business Media|first1=Inc}}</ref>\n* [[Australian Recording Industry Association|Australia]]: 1997<ref name=\"Australian Certifications\">{{cite web|url=http://www.aria.com.au/pages/aria-charts-accreditations.htm|title=ARIA Charts \u2013 Accreditations|publisher=[[Australian Recording Industry Association]]|accessdate=September 15, 2009}}</ref> (online certification-database has begun since 1997. Certifications; however, exist